title: Ajnabee
subTitle: Raj and Priya befriend their new neighbours Vicky and Sonia. One day, Raj wakes up in Vicky's house and finds out that Sonia is killed and he is framed for it.

title: Dulhan Banu Main Teri
subTitle: Deepak, a wealthy expatriate, faces family opposition as he pursues a romance with Radha, a woman from humble origins, whilst navigating cultural expectations and class divides.

title: Ram Aur Shyam
subTitle: Ram escapes from his home when he learns that his abusive brother-in-law plans to kill him. Justice is meted out when Shyam, Ram's long-lost twin, accidentally takes his place.

title: Sohni Mahiwal
subTitle: Mirza falls in love with Sohni, the daughter of a potter but their relationship is not accepted and he is thrown out of the village. Later, he starts meeting her disguised as a shepherd.

title: M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story
subTitle: M S Dhoni, a boy from Ranchi, aspires to play cricket for India. Though he initially tries to please his father by working for the Indian Railways, he ultimately decides to chase his dreams.

title: Mujrim
subTitle: Yashoda, a widow, brings up her children with love and honesty. However, she is disappointed when her son Shankar is arrested for breaking the law and disowns him.

title: Yeshwant
subTitle: Yeshwant, an honest police inspector, is framed and arrested for a murder. However, after being released from prison, he learns that his wife is having an affair.

title: Ziddi
subTitle: Deva, a vigilant young man, quickly climbs amongst the ranks of criminals in his city. However, things get complicated when he is framed for the assassination attempt of the CM.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Twins Amit and Kishan are separated at birth. However, when their paths cross in the future, together they work their way through and strive to overcome challenges.

title: Guru
subTitle: Guru, an ambitious man, along with his wife, leaves his small village behind to pursue his dream of opening his own business.

title: Bal Ganesh 3
subTitle: Dhoti, Topi and Suit Boot are more than happy to oblige when a group of alien kids come over to listen to adventure stories about their favourite Bal Ganesh.

title: Raja Babu
subTitle: Raja, a rich but illiterate young man, falls for Madhu after seeing her photographs and she mistakes him for a lawyer. Things turn ugly when she discovers the truth, leading to chaos and heartbreak.

title: Chandni
subTitle: Rohit sets out to find his former lover, whom he leaves due to his accident. When he meets her, he finds out she is engaged to marry her boss.

title: Izzatdaar
subTitle: When Brahm Dutt, a wealthy businessman, is falsely convicted on murder charges, he enlists the help of a boy to exact revenge on Indrajeet, his cruel son-in-law and the cause of all his miseries.

title: Sainik
subTitle: When Lieutenant Suraj goes missing, his father believes he is dead and decides to keep the news from his daughter and his son's wife. However, they already know and choose to put up a brave front.

title: Arjun Pandit
subTitle: A mild-mannered professor's world shatters after betrayal drives him into a violent transformation, where love and rage collide on the streets of Mumbai.

title: Housefull 2
subTitle: Four men join hands to date and marry the women of their dreams by changing their identities and deceiving their prospective fathers-in-law.

title: Tejaa
subTitle: Tejaa's family gets murdered when he is a child. Later, in an attempt to seek revenge, he traces down the three goons who were responsible.

title: Takkar
subTitle: Ravi Malhotra, a photographer, is framed by a corrupt policeman, D'Costa, on the day before his wedding. While in jail, Ravi studies law to exact revenge against his perpetrator.

title: Pyar Ke Do Pal
subTitle: Twins Sunil and Anil try to reunite their parents who separated many years ago due to a tragic misunderstanding regarding a friend's wish to have an abortion.

title: Suhagan
subTitle: Janki's life changes when she leaves her obsolete married life and runs away with Murli. However, trouble ensues when Murli commits suicide.

title: Main Hoon Na
subTitle: Major Ram is given orders to go undercover as a college student to protect a general's daughter from a rogue soldier. He must also fulfil his dying father's desire to reconcile with his family.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Yodha
subTitle: Karan, a lawyer, and Suraj, a victim of fate, find themselves fighting for the same cause when they take on the anti-social elements to rid the society of its ills.

title: Deewana Tere Naam Ka
subTitle: Friends Shankar and Shambhu share a lot in common and also end up falling in love with the same girl. However, when the girl loves Shankar, Shambhu parts ways with him and joins his rival.
